{"id":232949235,"title":"詢問N2單字書","content":"大家好👋🏻 先祝各位新年快樂！\n我想請問有通過N2的各位在準備N2時有買單字書來看嗎？\n\n去年12月我有報考N3，也順利的通過了\n但在這之前都沒有買過單字書，熟悉單字的來源大部分都是從Try!這本文法書以及NHK NEWS WEB EASY來的（主要是這個網站）\n\n這次想要報名7月的N2，但考量到很多人說N3跨到N2這中間的難度很高，我想只靠NHK NEWS WEB EASY的新聞來增加單字量應該不夠？\n\n所以想請教各位都有買單字書嗎？\n如果要買的話，哪一本比較好呢？\n我在ptt上看到有人推薦《新日檢完勝單語N2》和《新制對應 絕對合格！日檢單字N2》\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/05aa61ef-365a-43aa-ab29-19e5c87fa684/1280.jpeg\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/6d7d2afa-e92e-48db-8612-b2222529cc41/1280.jpeg\n\n請問這兩本好嗎？\n或是有其他單字本推薦呢？\n謝謝各位為我解惑！","excerpt":"大家好 先祝各位新年快樂！，我想請問有通過N2的各位在準備N2時有買單字書來看嗎？去年12月我有報考N3，也順利的通過了，但在這之前都沒有買過單字書，熟悉單字的來源大部分都是從Try！這本文法書以及N","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"ecc6a486-c4ac-4f76-996d-7dda5dcb8518","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-24T06:41:07.223Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-24T06:41:07.223Z","commentCount":9,"likeCount":12,"tags":[],"topics":["日語","日文","日檢"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"語言","forumAlias":"language","school":"國立聯合大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":12}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/05aa61ef-365a-43aa-ab29-19e5c87fa684/1280.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/6d7d2afa-e92e-48db-8612-b2222529cc41/1280.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"eee29825-3f32-4c56-86d5-94a97d5828a8","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/05aa61ef-365a-43aa-ab29-19e5c87fa684/640.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/05aa61ef-365a-43aa-ab29-19e5c87fa684/640.jpeg","thumbnail":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/05aa61ef-365a-43aa-ab29-19e5c87fa684/640.jpeg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":[],"createdAt":"2020-01-24T06:41:07.223